{"tid":1844323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】疫症爆發5日終封關！港府凌晨起禁湖北居民入境","createTime":"2020-01-26T14:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T20:18:50.000Z","uid":147522,"like":5,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"ec378c3d29bbb2516dad770698568d14dd05f28a","tid":1844323,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:51:01.000Z","msg":"港府宣佈限制湖北省居民以及任何過去14日到過湖北省的人士進入香港，特首林鄭月娥1月26日召開應對新型冠狀病毒感染疫情的督導委員會暨指揮中心會議。因應目前疫情主要在湖北省爆發而且越趨嚴峻，加上專家指隱性病人大大增加防控疫情的難度，督導委員會暨指揮中心決定限制湖北省居民以及任何過去14日到過湖北省的人士進入香港，直至另行通知為止，以減低感染者進入香港的機會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200126/3735474FK5CXWBYH2VOSD7TVCU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200126%2F3735474FK5CXWBYH2VOSD7TVCU%2F&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropFYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=6fb11680\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200126%2F3735474FK5CXWBYH2VOSD7TVCU%2F&h=bcc14804\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200126/3735474FK5CXWBYH2VOSD7TVCU/</a>"},{"pid":"7788e756a3aac20ba19a6c57b465e6e690e6ee6f","tid":1844323,"uid":194298,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:52:06.000Z","msg":"根本無可能知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378a02669581d0b723c55d367836c9bd950a3fb5","tid":1844323,"uid":163937,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:52:24.000Z","msg":"都入晒黎啦"},{"pid":"19464c2b1d0a999805a9297a3e62afe1bf5a902b","tid":1844323,"uid":89543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:53:23.000Z","msg":"限制定禁止？"},{"pid":"564966abcc94cdf8fd4980d29f02b35d423929fe","tid":1844323,"uid":311550,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:53:23.000Z","msg":"邊有封？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係扮做左野咋"},{"pid":"287c25a4e78b6a439e177c81511a35727b4d84d1",